# BankAccount Class

## Data Dictionary

| Attribute           | Data Type     | Description                          |
|---------------------|---------------|--------------------------------------|
| `accountNumber`     | `std::string` | Unique identifier for the account.   |
| `accountHolderName` | `std::string` | The name of the account owner.       |
| `balance`           | `double`      | The current monetary balance.        |

## Methods List

| Method Signature                                     | Return Type   | Description                            |
|------------------------------------------------------|---------------|----------------------------------------|
| `bankAccount()`                                      | (Constructor) | Default constructor.                   |
| `bankAccount(string, string, double)`                | (Constructor) | Parameterized constructor.             |
| `getAccountHolderName() const`                       | `std::string` | Returns the owner's name.              |
| `getBalance() const`                                 | `double`      | Returns current balance.               |
| `setAccountHolderName(string)`                       | `void`        | Updates the owner's name.              |
| `deposit(double)`                                    | `void`        | Adds money to the balance.             |
| `withdraw(double)`                                   | `void`        | Subtracts money if funds are sufficient.|
